### Create a User
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Alice",
  "email": "alice@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Create a Project
POST http://localhost:8080/api/projects
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Team Dashboard",
  "description": "Real-time team tracking project"
}

### Create a Task
POST http://localhost:8080/api/tasks/project/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Setup backend",
  "description": "Build Spring Boot APIs",
  "status": "In Progress",
  "project": { "id": 1 }
}

### Fetch All Tasks
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tasks
